    "name": "Cavalier's Banner",
    "prerequisite": "*Cavalier Dedication*",
    "requirement": "You have pledged your service to a specific organization or ideal.",
    "subtype": "feat",
    "text": "You fly the banner of your pledge from your mount, raising your allies\u2019 spirits. You and all allies in a 30-foot emanation from your mount gain a +1 circumstance bonus to Will saves and DCs against fear effects. If your banner is destroyed or removed, allies within 30 feet become frightened 1.",
